	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001015_0001"/><!--pb/@n='25r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">8<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> May</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I enclose 
<lb/>a letter I got last night 
<lb/>from <persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Adams</persName><reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Would it be worth 
<lb/>while to send it 
<lb/>to the <placeName>Athenaeum</placeName>
<lb/>with a note requesting 
<lb/><del type="strikethrough">him</del><add place="above"><persName>Adams</persName></add> to send his 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001015_0002"/><!--pb/@n='25v'--> 
<lb/>photograph to the 
<lb/>detective police to 
<lb/>be dealt with in 
<lb/>the manner adopted 
<lb/>towards all who 
<lb/>have similar views 
<lb/>of honesty &amp; legality<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>The denial of 
<lb/>advertisements is 
<lb/>instructive as even 
<lb/>the authors of them 
<lb/>start back from 
<lb/>the deception 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001015_0003"/><!--pb/@n='26r'--> 
<lb/>practised when 
<lb/>they see it presented 
<lb/>to their own 
<lb/>eyes in print in 
<lb/>its naked deformity<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>The other parties 
<lb/>are I think equally 
<lb/>guilty for I was 
<lb/>never asked whether 
<lb/>I would permit 
<lb/>my letters to be 
<lb/>published in a 
<lb/>collective form 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001015_0004"/><!--pb/@n='26v'--> 
<lb/>by either the "Banner" 
<lb/>Snow - or the 
<lb/>L.M. Society. <persName>M<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Prout</persName>
<lb/>who furnished 
<lb/>my letters to the Banner 
<lb/>wrote a review in 
<lb/>it of <persName>Adam's</persName> work 
<lb/>&amp; told me he had 
<lb/>done so. My sister 
<lb/>says it is a case of 
<lb/>"Satan reproving sin" </p>
<lb/><p><persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/><p>It is mortifying to come from 
<lb/><placeName>Africa</placeName> to be so handled<reg>.</reg></p>
			
